  {
    "title": "Pre-book otherwise expect bad service and horrible food",
    "rating": 2,
    "travelDate": "2022-10",
    "publishedDate": "2022-10-17",
    "text": "DO NOT go to Crocodile Pools unless you have pre-booked. If you have booked in advance, you may get reasonable service and good food depending on the mood of the owner/manager and the chef.\nOverall the owner/ manager should NOT accept guests who have not pre-booked. Owner / manager treats walk-in guests with disdain provides crappy service AND crappy food but still takes your money as the food and drinks are very expensive. If you provide feedback indicating areas of improvement, he informs you that you should have pre-booked.\nThere is an undertone of ill-treatment of staff who are poor BLACK women hired mostly from Zimbabwe.",
    "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g293767-d17352556-r864919887-Crocodile_Pools_River_Safaris-Gaborone_South_East_District.html",
