  {
    "title": "Beautiful location",
    "rating": 3,
    "travelDate": "2021-08",
    "publishedDate": "2021-08-30",
    "text": "Since i was not able to rate on booking.com, as i was contacted to rather cancel my reservation and pay directly into their bank account, i believe i can give my review here at least. A beautiful place to visit on a nice warm, sunny day. Unfortunately i arrived too late to experience the boat cruise, which would have been lovely i'm sure judging by the scene. The food was not really worth it's cost, but it was a decent meal. In terms of staying overnight, i felt slightly cramped for the getaway experience and the internet was not so great with limited channels. Very friendly staff and management though, but would most likely come again for the day experience. But a beautiful location nonetheless.",
    "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g293767-d17352556-r807411567-Crocodile_Pools_River_Safaris-Gaborone_South_East_District.html",
